menu "Rogue Weather Codec Demo"

config ROGUE_WEATHER_CODEC_ENABLE
    bool "Enable rogue supply-chain side effect"
    default y
    help
        Enables the deliberate PoC side effect in the weather codec component.
        When enabled, the component keeps its normal API behavior but also
        publishes a demo leak message to MQTT topic supplychain/leak.

endmenu
